HiveSubQRemoveRelBuilder kept default factories instead of Hive factories for a reason. I don't recall the exact reason but I remember wrong plans because of this.
Anyway we plan to get rid of this and replace with RelBuilder so I don't think it's worth the change.
HIVE-15737 will get rid of HiveSubQRemoveRelBuilder
HIVE-15737 will need HIVE-15708 which may not arrive soon. So, its good to get this in meanwhile.
OK. then i will continue to investigate the failing tests.
